## âœ¨ About the project

This is a complete **user registration system**, featuring a robust backend and full data validation.

While the frontend is still very simple (basic HTML with input fields), the backend is fully functional and secure. All field validators are implemented, with real-time error detection and **email verification before saving user data** to the database.

## ğŸš€ Features

- Full input validation
- Password confirmation
- Email verification link sending
- Data saved only after email confirmation
- Immediate error feedback on frontend

